{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeAnnotations:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSArray","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSArray<id<MLNAnnotation>>"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"annotations"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"annotations","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The array of annotation objects to remove. Objects in the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"array must conform to the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Removing annotation objects dissociates them from the map view entirely,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"preventing them from being displayed on the map. Thus you would typically","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"call this method only when you want to hide or delete the given annotations.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1833","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","title":"removeAnnotations:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeAnnotations:"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeAnnotations:"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)removeAnnotations:"},"abstract":[{"text":"Removes an array of annotations from the map view, deselecting any selected","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"annotations in the array.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/removeAnnotations:"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/removeannotations:"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/removeAnnotations:":{"kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"removeAnnotations:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"removeAnnotations:","role":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/removeAnnotations:","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/removeannotations:","abstract":[{"text":"Removes an array of annotations from the map view, deselecting any selected","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"annotations in the array.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removeAnnotations:","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"title":"MLNMapView","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","title":"MLNAnnotation","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","title":"MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","kind":"symbol"}}}